  'Wu, S., Liu, Y., Southam, G., Robertson, L.M., Wykes, J., Yi, Q., Hall, M., Li, Z., Sun, Q., Saha, N., Chan, T.S. (2021). Rhizosphere drives biotite-like mineral weathering and secondary Fe-Si mineral formation in Fe ore tailings. ACS Earth and Space Chemistry, 5, 618-631.',
